VPC Peering
============
Two VPC can communicate with each other using VPC peering.

VPC peering is possible
1.Two different VPC in different aws account
2.Two different VPC in different region in same account
3.Two different VPC in same region.

Creating VPC peering isn't chargeable but data transfer across VPC is chargeable.

